The overall photo-degradation kinetics follows the first-order simplification of the Langmuir–Hinshelwood (L–H) mechanism, which is well established for photo-catalysis at low initial pollutant concentration (Ref.) The relevant equation is as follows (Eq. 8):8lnCCO=-kappt\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
